<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="2427">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$scone-mirror" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/scone-mirror" class="zg-link" title="Scone">Scone</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$kingdom-fading" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/kingdom-fading" class="zg-link" title="kingdom fading">kingdom fading</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$chen-zhong-6-84" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/chen-zhong-6-84" class="zg-link" title="陈重">陈重</a></span>
